Title: President
               Company: Ariel Investments LLC
Job Details
               Company Size: $25 mil to less than $50 mil - Employee Range: 100 to less than 500. Ariel Investments, LLC is a Chicago-based money management firm that serves individual investors and 401(k) plans through its no-load mutual funds and also manages separate accounts for institutional clients. Throughout its 25-year history, patience has served as the bedrock of Ariel's investment philosophy and approach to building the firm. By adhering to a consistent and disciplined approach, Ariel has grown from 2 to nearly 100 employees with $11 billion in assets under management. Today, Ariel has become much more than an investment management firm; it is a team of diverse and uniquely talented individuals who share a common mission of helping shareholders achieve their financial dreams while affecting positive change in the community.
