 Mellody Hobson


 
Producer





Mellody Hobson is a producer and executive, known for Un-Broke: What You Need to Know About Money (2009), CBS This Morning (2012) and The 40th Annual Daytime Emmy Awards (2013). She has been married to George Lucas since June 22, 2013. They have one child.            
See full bio »
            
 





